la&s;t, by de&s;i&s;ting from exerci&s;ing the Minin&s;terial Function within the Li|berties
of the Town of <HI>Edinburgh.</HI> To which they an&s;wer'd, that they
had de&s;i&s;ted for &s;ome time &s;ince that Sentence, but not altogether, it be|ing
